      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "[**9-14**] SPIKING FEVERS TO 104,REQUIRING    PRESSERS,WORSENING RF,ACIDOSIS,K T",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row415025#s8",
      "text": "[**9-14**] SPIKING FEVERS TO 104,REQUIRING    PRESSERS,WORSENING RF,ACIDOSIS,K TO 7,ARRHYTHMIAS,CRRT STARTED,TX I    UNIT PRBC    PMHX: cabg, AAA, gout, obesity, IDDM.crf    Renal failure, Chronic (Chronic renal failure, CRF, Chronic kidney    disease)    Assessment:    ACIDOSIS IMPROVING,CVVHD RUNNING WELL,CA,K REPLETED PER PROTOCL ,GOAL    EVEN BALANCE    Action:    Q6HR BLOOD WORK,    Response:    PT [**Name (NI) 1940**]    [**Name (NI) 171**]:    CONT, CRRT PER PROTOCOL,NOTIFY FELLOW C CONCERNS IF ANY    Sepsis, Severe (with organ dysfunction)    Assessment:    AFEBRILE ,BP STABLE ,LACTATE DECREASING ,STEROID DOSE DECREASED    ,PIPRICILLIN DC ,    Action:    WEANED OFF PRESSERS ,ANTI BX AS ORDERED ,BLOOD CX SENT ,1 UNIT PRBC    Response:    TOL PRESSER WEAN    Plan:    FOLLOW TEMP  CONTINUE ,ANTI BX  ,MONITOR VS    Cholangitis    Assessment:    CHOLE TUBE IRRIGATED ,DSD CHANGE  PER ORDERS ,PATENT DRAINING PURULENT    TAN ,SECURELY ANCHORED TO PT ,US  DONE    Plan:    MAINTAIN PATENCY ,INTACT DSD    Diabetes Mellitus (DM), Type I    Assessment:    HYPERGLYCEMIA,ON STEROIDS    Action:    INSULIN GTT    Response:    BS COMING UNDER CONTROL    Plan:    HOURLY BS ,TITRATE INSULIN AS NEEDED"
    }
  ],
